Package com.bakdata.dedupe.duplicate_detection

Interface PossibleDuplicateHandler<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the record
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
    @FunctionalInterface
public interface PossibleDuplicateHandler<T>
    A callback that is invoked when a Classification.POSSIBLE_DUPLICATE has been founds during DuplicateDetection.
